Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:04.79,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,Souls that once dwelled inside humans now dwell inside puppets and are lurching forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.73,0:24:04.89,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今　人形に宿り　闊歩する
