Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.75,0:24:11.72,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,Although their appearances are deformed, their souls are indeed human.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.83,0:24:08.09,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,姿形は　異形なれども
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:11.59,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その魂は　まさしく人間
